data.description: This charming ranch style 2 bedroom sits at the end of a quiet street nestled under a canopy of trees that shade the large fenced in back yard.  Perfect for those seeking a great investment as well as quick access to the airport and Marta.  Beautiful hardwood floors as well as a spacious eat in kitchen that overlooks a recessed bonus room perfect for a den.  Enjoy all that East Point has to offer while being a hop skip and a jump from Midtown Atlanta.  Roof replaced 6 years ago and the property has been lovingly maintained.
